---
description: Testing rules
globs: ["**/*.test.*", "**/tests/**", "apps/web/e2e/**"]
---
- Tests first for new behavior; tests assert behavior, not implementation details.
- Naming: `*.test.ts` / `*.test.tsx`, colocated under the module's `tests/` folder.
- Vitest projects: api-unit / web-unit / shared-unit / lint-rules; integration: api-integration (supertest).
- E2E: Playwright with mocked backend by default; never call real Gemini in CI.
- Coverage on touched modules, per file: 95 statements / 90 branches / 95 functions / 95 lines
  (critical paths near 100%). See testing/coverage-policy.md.
- Never skip/focus tests or lower thresholds to pass a gate. Coverage runs in pre-push.
- Standards live in testing/; reusable case matrices in test-cases/.
